{"tid":1033591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【電郵生成器請廣傳】檔案法諮詢   一人一信入爆法改會","createTime":"2019-02-23T09:39:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T05:05:11.000Z","uid":138409,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"89f8e0390adf3ad45dd3bc1410f09dc6aac6ba24","tid":1033591,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T09:39:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5c54TVE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5c54TVE.jpg&h=0d01835c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網址：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/PRAFOIA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FPRAFOIA&d=gMg1FBwAZA1XbJy1Uvmn1M0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=5e14fb1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/PRAFOIA</a><br />\n<br />\n本土研究社 Liber Research Community和香港眾志 Demosistō自前年發起「#香港前途研究計劃」，一眾年輕學人致力解密香港檔案，盼望透過民間研究為當下民主運動論述及中港問題提供扎實基礎，還公眾對香港前途談判的知情權。<br />\n<br />\n在挖掘檔案期間，我們深感現行公共檔案管理參差不齊，體會到港府縱容公共機構銷毀重要檔案，亦不准公眾查閱現存關鍵檔案。在缺乏立法監管的情況下，政府如同將公眾知情權置諸後腦。<br />\n<br />\n適逢法律改革委員會進行《檔案法》及公開資料諮詢，「香港前途研究計劃」呼籲各位參與一人一信行動，在<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>限期屆滿（三月五日）</strong></span></span>前以電郵生成器去信法改會，促請政府訂立有效規管政府機關的《檔案法》，並落實具透明度的《資訊自由法》打破黑箱。<br />\n__________________________<br />\n█ 解密過去🔓重掌未來 █<br />\n💰捐款支持：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2IVW56L\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IVW56L&d=gMg1FBwAZA1XbJy1Uvmn1M0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=bc5a11e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2IVW56L</a><br />\n📖研究成果：<a href=\"https://medium.com/@decodinghkshistory\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40decodinghkshistory&d=gMg1FBwAZA1XbJy1Uvmn1M0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=3ca356de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@decodinghkshistory</a><br />\n🗂計劃詳情：<a href=\"https://researchforfuture.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresearchforfuture.hk%2F&d=gMg1FBwAZA1XbJy1Uvmn1M0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=f3de51fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://researchforfuture.hk/</a><br />\n📧聯絡 #香港前途研究計劃： <a href=\"http://m.me/decodinghkhistory\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.me%2Fdecodinghkhistory&d=gMg1FBwAZA1XbJy1Uvmn1M0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=de356f73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">m.me/decodinghkhistory</a>"},{"pid":"95d5a48ee5a296e88ff764d728915d1f1fe7968c","tid":1033591,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T09:44:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"59da3c4534f106862928e6ef037ca3864a56c239","tid":1033591,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T04:40:52.000Z","msg":"倒數4日<br />\n3月5日截止<br />\n求各位幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\npush"},{"pid":"b63b25fc6c8244c22b28b2e6e3e5e40877aa0831","tid":1033591,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T04:41:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2285211515081001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2285211515081001&d=gMg1FBwAZA1XbJy1Uvmn1M0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=83f21074\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2285211515081001</a>"},{"pid":"b644a8318854677180fdf3a3b638f3f11988e43d","tid":1033591,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T04:43:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9a2c3c7f39ef4dfafd4cf163af704d5db17b0a4c","tid":1033591,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T04:50:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3885e69698ec61fe9a8246fca7f3a9fdfa229168","tid":1033591,"uid":138409,"like":0,"d